<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{Post Title}</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inconsolata:wght@300;400;500&family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="page-wrapper">
        <header class="site-header">
            <img class="site-author" src="Assets/fpo-author.jpg" alt="Will Shaheen">
            <h1>Will's Fancy Tech Blog</h1>
            <div>
                <nav>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Dashboard</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
                <button>Log-In/Sign-Up</button>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="page-content">
            <main>
                <article>
                    <header>
                        <h2>{Post Title}</h2>
                        <p class="byline">Will Shaheen</p>
                        <time datetime="YYYY-MM-DD">YYYY-MM-DD</time>
                    </header>
                    <div>
                        <p>
                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nostrum, quae nisi, eveniet ipsam
                            eum iste labore similique, minima at ex fugiat perspiciatis! Provident dolorem obcaecati
                            expedita debitis ipsum quia voluptas?
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </main>
            <aside>
                <section>
                    <h3>Recent Comments</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Username - Comment (Max 30 char)</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3>Archive</h3>
                    <ol>
                        <li><a href="#">April 2021</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">March 2021</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">February 2021</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">January 2021</a></li>
                    </ol>
                </section>
            </aside>
        </div>

        <footer class="site-footer">
            <p>
                &copy; 2021 - Will Shaheen. All&nbsp;Rights&nbsp;Reserved.
            </p>
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>

</html>